-- Mets Place Pitcher Santana on Disabled List With Ankle Sprain
-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 2012-07-21T15:59:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-21/mets-place-pitcher-santana-on-disabled-list-with-ankle-sprain.html
The  New York Mets  placed starting
pitcher Johan Santana on the 15-day disabled list with a right
ankle sprain, the Major League Baseball team said in a
statement.  The 33-year-old lefthander has a record of 6 wins and 7
losses this season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  